description: The fund invests at least 80% of its net assets in financial instruments, securities of the index, and ETFs that track the index and other financial instruments that provide daily leveraged exposure to the index or to ETFs that track the index. The index measures the performance of U.S. and Canadian stocks that are classified in the application software, systems software and home entertainment software sub-industries of the GICS information technology sector. It is non-diversified.
name: Direxion Daily S&P Expanded Tech Software Sector Bull 2X Shares
